	(text "max at max atten.\n0.5V to 4.5V @10% \n= (0.5V to 4.5V) * 0.1\n= 0.05V to 0.45V\n\ntyp. at part. atten.\n1.54V to 3.46V @25% \n= (1.54V to 3.46V) * 0.25\n= 0.385 V to 0.865V\n\nmin at min atten.\n2.45V to 2.55V @100% \n= (2.45V to 2.55V) * 0.1\n= 2.45V to 2.55V"
